32
00:01:51.570 --> 00:01:55.840
So if I took a bunch of flashlights,
if I had a flashlight that was red,

33
00:01:55.840 --> 00:01:58.010
a flashlight that was green,
and a flashlight that was blue,

34
00:01:58.010 --> 00:02:01.870
