with Photoshop or Illustrator,

57
00:03:19.778 --> 00:03:23.390
or anything like that and it asks you
the color mode that you're working in.

58
00:03:23.390 --> 00:03:25.430
You're always working in
a color mode whether or

59
00:03:25.430 --> 00:03:30.150
not you're deciding to, it always has
a defined preset for a color mode.

60
